      <title>Workday 警告软件行业“销售审查将加强”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/workday-slips-after-company-cuts-subscription-sales-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在软件公司Workday Inc.下调了全年订阅收入预期并表示客户对订单更加谨慎之后，该公司股价出现八年多来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/workday-slips-after-company-cuts-subscription-sales-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 20:43:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
